                    <p>
                        Rewatch, and the folks at Rewatch, taught Mike more about design, engineering, strategy, and leadership in a year than he had ever learned before. Due to Rewatch's small size and product focused on better communication, Mike was given visibility into and built relationships with various departments, and their goals/pain points, like he'd never experienced prior.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The nimble size of Rewatch also provided Mike with more responsibility. He was the sole marketing designer/developer and had to find ways to execute any project in that realm, even those he is less comfortable with, efficiently and with style.
